160
00:09:14,179 --> 00:09:18,019
So every agent gets a verifiable,
non-shareable identity.

161
00:09:18,329 --> 00:09:23,589
Shared credentials between agent instances
create accountability gaps that you

162
00:09:23,629 --> 00:09:25,329
