163
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:26,569
So scoped authorization.

164
00:09:26,569 --> 00:09:29,449
Permission scoped to the task under.

165
00:09:29,469 --> 00:09:33,709
So re-- so a summarization
agent should never hold write

166
00:09:33,709 --> 00:09:35,539
access to a production database.

167
00:09:35,549 --> 00:09:36,909
So it should have only read access.

168
00:09:37,409 --> 00:09:42,389
So similarly the role and access
should tie to the specific task

169
00:09:42,449 --> 00:09:44,389
