170
00:09:44,889 --> 00:09:46,079
Audit and traceability.

171
00:09:46,119 --> 00:09:50,939
So every agent action should be
audited traced across what it is

172
00:09:50,939 --> 00:09:54,979
doing so that it can be used for the
investigation or for the compliance

173
00:09:54,979 --> 00:10:01,009
purpose So if you cannot answer which
identity did the task then there is

174
00:10:01,009 --> 00:10:03,679
no agent security in the environment.

175
00:10:04,239 --> 00:10:09,549
Or even if you further say-- if we
cannot say that if the agent was

176
00:10:09,619 --> 00:10:14,429
