it, then we don't have a sound agent

177
00:10:14,989 --> 00:10:18,239
life cycle policy or agent governance.

178
00:10:18,739 --> 00:10:21,899
So centralized-- so how we can achieve it?

179
00:10:21,909 --> 00:10:25,959
So centralized identity
governance, resilience by design.

180
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:32,389
So distributed siloed identity creates
