182
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:43,309
So we need to make sure there is
detection containment, and recovery.

183
00:10:43,849 --> 00:10:44,209
Okay?

184
00:10:44,509 --> 00:10:47,839
So centralized telemetry spots
anomalous behavior, which

185
00:10:47,839 --> 00:10:49,259
