186
00:10:49,739 --> 00:10:53,679
So-- And then for containment, you
should have one governance plane

187
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:55,459
where you should cut it down.

188
00:10:55,539 --> 00:10:57,719
I, I would term it as a AI kill switch.

189
00:10:57,949 --> 00:11:02,409
So unless there is a governance plane,
you cannot revoke the credential or kill

190
00:11:02,409 --> 00:11:05,679
